rhull.", "Kast et tomt malingsspann i en elv eller i fj\u00e6ra, og du risikerer en saftig bot. \u00c5 t\u00f8mme titusener tonn gift rett p\u00e5 havet, som rommer v\u00e5re rikeste og viktigste \u00f8kosystemer, er derimot greit. Om du heter Marine Harvest, Ler\u00f8y, Grieg Seafood eller Cermaq.", "At dette skjer i et rikt demokrati som v\u00e5rt er uverdig. Elisabeth Aspaker st\u00e5r smilende og blander en giftig cocktail. Derfor liker jeg ikke henne."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e510ce36a9d64384c9461b65f6e43102d7b676e0e0cbfd61b8cc0f22e1cf5cc2"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-14T19:27:47.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Fiskeriminister Elisabeth Aspaker er en trussel mot artsmangfoldet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article11882972.ece/9m7mqk/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_Elisabeth_Aspaker.jp_1_1_2U7Q2PJ.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/1b7d7b19c05257e0d3de7b88f8459b7ccc0f741b.jpg?58dcbf30"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Lutefisk rett fra havet -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "1b7d7b19c05257e0d3de7b88f8459b7ccc0f741b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "meninger"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["grieg seafood", "cermaq", "marine harvest"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "oppdrett"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["milj\u00f8direktoratet", "ler\u00f8y"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ellen ham